'{
 "blocks":[
   {"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Why CSS Performance Matters"},
   {"type":"paragraph","text":"CSS plays a major role in how browsers render and display pages. Inefficient styles can delay rendering and cause layout instability."},
   {"type":"paragraph","text":"Optimizing CSS improves both perceived and actual performance."},
   {"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Optimization Strategies"},
   {"type":"list","items":[
     "Reduce unused CSS.",
     "Avoid deep selector nesting.",
     "Use modern layout systems like Flexbox and Grid.",
     "Minimize expensive layout calculations."
   ]}
 ]
}',
'https://placehold.co/1200x630/0ea5e9/ffffff?text=CSS+Performance',
NULL,
NULL,
'published',
'2026-05-03',
'CSS Performance Optimization | Web Performance Guide',
'Discover how optimizing CSS improves page rendering speed and user experience.'
),

